    /**
     * * Write a function to find whether all the given tuples have equal length or not.
     *
     * > getEqual([[11, 22, 33], [44, 55, 66]], 3)
     * "All tuples have same length"
     * > getEqual([[1, 2, 3], [4, 5, 6, 7]], 3)
     * "All tuples do not have same length"
